Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 发现什么情况了吗？上尉 - 没有，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Anything, lieutenant? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经试过戴内瓦星上所有主要的传输站了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've tried every major transmitting station on Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一个回应我的通话请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None of them have acknowledged my contact signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,试试GSK-783，子空间频率3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try GSK-783, subspace frequency three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，长官，那是一个私人传输站的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, sir, that's a call sign for a private transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚，上尉，试试吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm very well aware of that, lieutenant. Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，说说你的看法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evaluation, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，据我推测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As I speculated, captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样大规模摧毁文明的疯狂行径\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the overall pattern of mass insanity destroying civilizations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大致发生在这部分星系的一条直线上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}follows an almost straight line through this section of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，有着古老文明的波托兰贝塔星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Over here, the Beta Portolan system, the ancient civilizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,考古学家们给我们的信息指出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Archaeologists have given us information indicating
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是这次暴行的开端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they were the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,两百年前，拉维尼娅5号星被劫掠一空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two hundred years ago, Lavinius V was swept by mass insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是天鹅座西塔12号星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then Theta Cygni XII.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,最近一次是发生在两年前的英格拉姆B星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The last was Ingraham B, two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这条路线的下一站，是戴内瓦星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And next in line, Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，你觉得这是由什么引起的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones, what's your theory about the cause of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用医学或科学来解释发生在那些星球上的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no medical or scientific cause for what happened on those planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这种行为有很明显的趋势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it follows a definite pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,从一颗行星…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a systematic progression from planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- …到另一颗行星的星系推进 - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...to planet. - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在监视器里发现一艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're picking up a ship on our sensors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.98,0:01:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝着戴内瓦太阳星飞去，飞船会烧毁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}heading directly into the Denevan sun. He'll burn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生，用曲速8前进，准备拦截\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plot an interception course, Mr. Sulu. Warp factor 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,马乎拉上尉，快联络那艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura, try to contact that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，那是艘戴内瓦外形的单人飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship is a one-man vessel of Denevan configuration, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不像是飞船失控，他的航向直指向太阳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He does not seem to be out of control. His course is straight for the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，用牵引波束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, tractor beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，超出传输范围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Out of range, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们取得联络了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Making contact, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,戴内瓦号，这里是联邦星舰进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Denevan ship, this is the USS Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否可以调转你的航向？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you reverse your course?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们离太阳越来越近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, we'll get too close to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,戴内瓦号，调转你的航向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Denevan ship, reverse your course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,调转你的航向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reverse your course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰外壳温度已达到480度，并且在持续上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Outer hull temperature, now 480 degrees and rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，他靠太近了 - 我们也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's too close, captain. - So are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,外壳温度达到1000度，并且在持续上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hull temperature, 1,000 degrees and rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳的重力牵引在不断增加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sun's gravimetric pull increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我做到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它终于死了！我自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's finally gone! I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，飞船着火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He burned up, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,调转航向，180度左右\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reverse course, 180 degrees about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，一切正常，星舰外壳温度正在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All clear, captain. Hull temperature falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,重力牵引下降到可接受水平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gravimetric pull approaching tolerance level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,将速度降低到亚曲速\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reduce to sub-warp speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去戴内瓦星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take us to Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘戴内瓦飞船是故意飞向太阳的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That Denevan ship headed deliberately into the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？ - 有一种可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why? - There's one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大规模疯狂灾难也许已经蔓延到这颗星球了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The mass insanity may have reached this planet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我现在不能向戴内瓦星发送信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I'm having difficulty on that transmitter call to Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续联络 - 是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Keep trying. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你哥哥山姆，他们一家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, your brother, Sam, his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是定居在这颗星球上吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}aren't they stationed on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: to explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00DA4E&}-=THE LAST FANTASY=-\N荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：sholto\N校对：诸星龟龟{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二十九集\N歼灭行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3287.2\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3287.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们追踪到的那场横扫星系这块区域的大规模暴行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The mass insanity we have tracked across this section
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎已经蔓延到戴内瓦星了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of the galaxy seems to have already touched Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那颗星球，在一百多年前被开辟成殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That planet, colonised over a century ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个星系最美丽的星球之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is one of the most beautiful in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这个星球的发展历程很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Planet development is normal, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,起初作为这片区域的运输线基地被开辟为殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Originally colonised as a freighting line base in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，他们定期从这里出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, they make regular trips from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为小行星带的矿工们运输物资\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}carrying supplies to the asteroid belt for the miners
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,并把货物运出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and bringing cargo out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,作为工程顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've made the run a couple of times myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己做过好几次运输\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as an engineering advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,超过一年没有和联邦联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No Federation contacts for over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，我已经和你的私人传输站取得了联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've made contact with your private transmitter, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,接到扩音器上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put it on audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请快点来，救救我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please hurry. Help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有时间了，他们会知道的，求你了！求——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't have much time. They'll know. Please! Please--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰，我是吉姆，在进取号上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aurelan. This is Jim on the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,重复你说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Repeat your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官，通话断了 - 再联络\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Contact broken, sir. - Re-establish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉，长官 - 我对你的道歉不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm sorry, sir. - I'm not interested in your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再联络那个传输站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Re-establish contact with that transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，恐怕现在不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid that's impossible at the moment, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他们立即停止广播了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They stopped broadcasting immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有回应我的联络信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They do not acknowledge my contact signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续试着联络他们 - 是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Keep trying to raise them. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认识那个女人吗？ - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Did you know who that woman was? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说中了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were right a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥山姆住在戴内瓦星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My brother, Sam, lives on Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个研究生物学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a research biologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像是他的妻子奥瑞兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounded like his wife, Aurelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的相位枪设为击昏模式，我们将直接传送到首都\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Set your phasers on stun. We'll beam directly into the capital city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,保持警戒状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alert status.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉上尉对信号的追踪没什么进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura has had no further response to our signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感应装置报告在星球表面发现了很多人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensors report the expected number of humans on the planet surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，他们表现地异常平静，极少有活动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, they are strangely quiet, very little activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要了解到底在那座星球上发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll want a complete transcript of everything that happens down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命，长官 - 我们出发吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,开始传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,戴内瓦星上大约有一百万居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are almost a million inhabitants of Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,单单这座城市里就有10万多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's more than 100,000 in this city alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人都到哪里去了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，他们在建筑物里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're here, captain. In the buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里安静地让人害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strangely quiescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥的实验室就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My brother's lab is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们曾给我们发送过信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They signalled us once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那里一定有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There should be someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去看看发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's find out what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，有几个人向我们接近了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, several people approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,退后，赶快走，退后！我们不想伤害你们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go back! Run, get away! We don't want to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 退后！ - 离开！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Go back! - Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 退后！ - 快离开这里！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Go back! - Get out of here, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑，离开这里！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Run! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 走开，快离开这里！ - 快离开这里！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Go away! Get out of here now! - Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快跑，离开这里！ - 我们不想伤害你们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Run! Get away! - We don't want to hurt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,准备开火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,开火！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你听到他们说的话吗？ - 听到了，他们好像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Did you hear what they said? - Indeed. They seemed concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 担心我们的安全 - 但他们想用这些棒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- for our safety. - They tried to brain us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们的脑壳敲开，老骨头，检查下他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with these clubs. Check them out, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的思维和行动不一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their attitude was inconsistent with their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,至少说明一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，这里出状况了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's something wrong, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的神经系统…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their nervous systems...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不清醒，他们应该是身不由己地行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unconscious like this, there should be just routine autonomic activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我能看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I'm getting a very high reading,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,即使在他们不清醒的内心里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as though, even in their unconscious state,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也深受刺激影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they're being violently stimulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,散开，跟着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fan out. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,警戒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了，他们来了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're here! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，不要让他们过来！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, keep them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们来了！ - 奥瑞兰，我是吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They're here! - Aurelan, it's Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们来了！ - 奥瑞兰，我是吉姆，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- They're here! - It's Jim, Aurelan. Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aurelan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，这是你哥哥吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this your brother, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实是我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经的哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男孩神志不清，但还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The boy's unconscious, but he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,皮特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我最好还是把这个男孩和他母亲带回飞船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd better get the boy and the mother back to the ship, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里不能给他们治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't do much for them down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，准备传送到星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get ready to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy to Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,准备传送四个人到星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prepare to beam up party of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我理解你——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I understand how you--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，谢谢你，麦考伊先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. Yes, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你也听见了我嫂子说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You heard my sister-in-law say something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她说“他们”在这里，你怎么看？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about "they" being here. Your guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，注意通风设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Notice the ventilator, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很明显是想要阻止什么东西进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, they were trying to keep something outside from getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然，他们没有成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Obviously, they were not entirely successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这讲不通，报告没有说这里有有害生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That doesn't make sense. There are no harmful life forms reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的传感系统未收集到不属于这里的生物信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our sensors didn't pick up anything that didn't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对，我也很不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is correct. I am at a loss to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们准备好传送了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to beam up, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你嫂子恢复意识时，你也能在船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like you to be onboard when your sister-in-law regains consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你来掌管登陆部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take charge of the landing party, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要找到一切的起因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want some answers to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在我没有把实验室的金属板放回位置之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't be able to give you the exact cause
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能给你确切的答复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until I get the plates back from the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都很痛苦，我给他们注射了镇定剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're both in extreme pain. I've sedated them heavily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你嫂子的身体像是有很强的抗性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But your sister-in-law seems to have a high tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,镇定剂对她没起多少作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The tranquilizer hasn't affected her much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她能说话吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can she talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aurelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰，我是吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aurelan, it's Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆，他…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam. He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的儿子还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But your son's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你得帮助我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，真的是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is you, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰，你得告诉我们发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to tell us what happened, Aurelan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你和其他人都遭遇了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They came...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…在八个月前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...eight months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,难以言说的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖的东西！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Horrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,游客用飞船把他们从一颗行星带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Visitors brought them in their vessel from a planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,英格拉姆B星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ingraham B.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么样的东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那并不是船员们的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not the ship's crew's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那些东西控制着他们来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The things made them bring their ship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,奥瑞兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aurelan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我是什么样的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's important that you tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我们很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what kind of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是他们的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,当她回答问题时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When she answers questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,任何问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}any questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要挣扎着才能说出答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's as if she's fighting to get the answers out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像有东西为了阻止她说话而不断制造疼痛感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As though something is exerting pain to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是用疼痛来控制我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They use it to control us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，他们还在扩散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're spreading, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们利用我们做宿体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They need us to be their arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们强迫我们为他们建造飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're forcing us to build ships for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让他们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让他们继续肆虐下去了！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't let them go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我兄长的儿子…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My brother's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我会竭尽所能救他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll do everything I can, Jim, to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 报告情况 - 道路异常安静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Report. - The streets are extraordinarily quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没见到其它戴内瓦星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've seen no other Denevans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那些我们先前击晕的人在我们出来时就不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the ones we stunned earlier were gone when we came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到过其它生物吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen some kind of creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,长得像外星人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}any alien form?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，长官，这里只有我们听到的噪声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}None, sir. There's just that noise we heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一种特殊的嗡嗡响声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A peculiar buzzing sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚要去检查下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were about to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去看看那是什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的相位枪调到可以杀伤的3级功率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Set your phasers on force 3, to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去寻找某种生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're looking for some kind of creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经了解到它很危险，能致人死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we already know it will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,围成一个圆圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Form a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,开火！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真不可思议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它不但没有被相位枪摧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not only should it have been destroyed by our phasers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的三录仪都没有它的相关记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it does not even register on my tricorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，它甚至看起来都不像是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, it doesn't even look real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我们的认知，它没有生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is not life as we know or understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然而很明显，它活着，它存在着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yet it is obviously alive, it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它能够抵抗相位枪最大功率射击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it can bear up under full phaser power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我建议冒险把它带到船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I suggest we risk taking it aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里太靠近它了，这或许是个圈套，我们快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's too closed in here. It may be a trap. Let's move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了，你能站起来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's gone. Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你还好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不管那种生物是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever the creatures are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然他们控制住了戴内瓦星上所有的居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they have apparently taken over all the inhabitants of Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，舰队医疗官麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meanwhile, ship surgeon Dr. McCoy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,正在检查那只生物在史波克先生背上留下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is examining a strange puncture wound
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪刺穿伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}left by one of the creatures on Mr. Spock's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是第二次试图从他的身体里取出那东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the second time he's come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是他抗拒我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Either he's fighting us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,…就是他身体里的东西在抗拒我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...or something inside of him is fighting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，即使在史波克先生身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, the readings have never looked like that before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的数据也非比寻常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not even on Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,准备缝合伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's prepare to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,护士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我们不应该就这样结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, that's not all you're going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 查佩尔小姐 - 医生，还有更多的东西在他身体里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Miss Chapel. - Doctor, there is more of it in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,盘根错节，遍布身体每个部位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}entwined all through his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,查佩尔小姐，如果你不能像我要求的那样协助我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Chapel, if you cannot assist me as required,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就叫其他护士过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}call another nurse in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要么协助我，要么叫其他人来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But do one or the other now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说，吉姆，我不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To be very frank, Jim, I don't know that I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我能为史波克或你的侄子做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for Spock or your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那种生物的组织切片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pieces of some form of living tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我从史波克的脊髓中取出一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I removed one from Spock's spinal cord,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的都是从你嫂子身体里取的，都是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the other from your sister-in-law's body. They're both the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你侄子太虚弱了不能动手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The boy's far too weak to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，据我所知，移除这些组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Besides, the removal of the tissue
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,并不能免除疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}wouldn't stop the pain anyhow, as far as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你及时为史波克做手术了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you operate on Spock in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，我只是移除了部分组织来检测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, no. I just removed these for examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他的身体里都是这样的触须\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His body's full of these tentacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,缠绕并在他的神经系统滋长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}entwining and growing all about his nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的侄子呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My nephew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他的情况也是那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显的，当那种生物攻击时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Evidently, when the creature attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,会留下一根刺，就像蜜蜂或黄蜂那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it leaves a stinger, much like a bee or a wasp,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在受伤者身体里留下身体的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}leaving one of these in the victim's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然后它会迅速掌控受伤者的身体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it takes over the victim very rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且与身体结合得非常非常紧密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the entwining is far, far too involved
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于常规的外科手术不能移除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for conventional surgery to remove.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么建议吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,实验室，科学部…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The lab, the science departments...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们都束手无策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we're all stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不会屈服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥，这里是医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge, this is Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉麦考伊医生，史波克先生刚离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell Dr. McCoy Mr. Spock just left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他有些发狂，可能会对人造成危害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's delirious, possibly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所有船员，安全戒备状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All decks, security alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找到并制止史波克先生，他可能很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Locate and restrain Mr. Spock. He may be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要的话，用相位枪将他击昏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Use phasers, on stun, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一定要控制飞船 - 史波克——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Must take ship. - Spock--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,…驾驶飞船降落！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把他送回医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get him back to the Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,用束缚带绑牢他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Use security restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,K-3指示器记录了疼痛的程度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The K-3 indicator registers the level of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,当我打开它时，注意观察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, watch it as I turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看，这就是他所经历的疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, that's what he's been going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过这样的事，难怪这个可怜的家伙会发狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never seen anything like it. No wonder the poor devils go mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要束缚带了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These restraints will no longer be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我也不需要镇定剂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nor will your sedatives, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我能回归自己的岗位了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be able to return to duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我为先前的被软弱控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I apologise for my weakness earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,试图控制飞船而道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I tried to take control of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I simply did not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你有什么不理解的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is there to understand, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我是个瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a Vulcan, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,疼痛是心理的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pain is a thing of the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而心理是可以被控制的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The mind can be controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是半个瓦肯人，你还是会受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're only half Vulcan. What about the human half of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它给我造成了不便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is proving to be an inconvenience,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是可以解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it is manageable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个生物，用它数以千计的触须\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The creature, with all of its thousands of parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是现在，还在压迫我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even now is pressuring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.97,0:24:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它想要这艘星舰，但我在顽强抵抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wants this ship. But I am resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，他真的能控制住自己吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can he control it the way he says, Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who knows, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.43,0:24:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解那个生物在他身上产生的疼痛感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know the amount of pain the creature can inflict upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是史波克是否能一直控制住自己…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But whether he can control it, hour to hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我有自己的意愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have my own will, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我来帮你吧 - 史波克，我很需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let me help. - I need you, Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们不能冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we can't take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:25:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要再观察你一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll keep you confined for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.87,0:25:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能够…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.13,0:25:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,…持续地控制自己的情绪…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...maintain control...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.38,0:25:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…我们会看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.18,0:25:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我的侄子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.89,0:25:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他恢复了意识，他是否也会经历那样的痛苦？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he regains consciousness, will he go through that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.98,0:25:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不管付出什么代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't care what it takes or costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你都得帮帮他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you've got to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.69,0:25:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你难道忘记了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.86,0:25:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面的星球上有超过100万居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are over a million colonists on that planet down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.53,0:25:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救他们同样是你的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just as much your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They need your help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.77,0:26:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个瓦肯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.49,0:26:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会感觉到疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.56,0:26:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.94,0:26:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你还待在医务室观察呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you were still confined to Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.48,0:26:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我康复了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.90,0:26:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,站住，你要到哪里去？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, now. Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去星球表面一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have an errand on the planet surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我传送到先前的同一坐标点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will beam me down to the same coordinates as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not likely, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.00,0:27:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特先生，这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is an order, Mr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.92,0:27:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.33,0:27:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但抱歉，我不得不违背它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm sorry I have to disobey it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.13,0:27:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长命令说不准任何人传送下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain said no one was to transport down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.39,0:27:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,站在那里别动，史波克先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Freeze right there, Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.14,0:27:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,…不然我就开枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...or I'll put you to sleep for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.20,0:27:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是传送室的史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Mr. Scott in the Transporter Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接通舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get me the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.88,0:27:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，我曾命令你待在医务室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, I gave you an order to stay in the Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.30,0:28:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,直到疼痛消失，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until the pain was gone, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.63,0:28:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经重新掌控了身体的主导权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has been discontinued, by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.30,0:28:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.06,0:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，他说他要到星球表面上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He said he was transporting down to the surface, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.35,0:28:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而你下命令，除非有你的授权，否则没人能传送下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your orders were that no one was to beam down unless you authorised it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.56,0:28:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉史波克先生已经下定决心了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And knowing Mr. Spock's determination on some things,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想最好还是在询问过你之前，把他留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought I'd better hold him here until I got your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.78,0:28:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，一定要抓住一只那种生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of the creatures will have to be captured
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.95,0:28:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才能对它进行分析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and analyzed, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.87,0:28:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在我被袭击之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We did not have a clear opportunity to do so earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.49,0:28:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有这样的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when I was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.29,0:28:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我的神经系统已经被感染了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since my nervous system is already affected,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.87,0:28:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你指出的那样，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as you pointed out, doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.21,0:28:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得它们能对我再造成什么伤害了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe they could do much more to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.21,0:28:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，这很荒谬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, this is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.63,0:28:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想我的病人到处乱跑，他应该躺在床上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want my patients running around. He should be in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.76,0:28:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我能完全掌控自己的意识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am in complete control of myself, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我既然能站在这里，就说明我不需要再待在床上了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fact that I am here proves that I do not belong in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.56,0:28:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.98,0:28:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的逻辑，一如往常…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your logic, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.36,0:29:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…让人不能辩驳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...is inescapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.03,0:29:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,把他传送下去，要和我们保持紧密联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beam him down. Stay in constant touch with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.62,0:29:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的相位枪给他，他会需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give him your phaser. He'll need that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,开始传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.03,0:29:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，史波克很虚弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, that man is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.28,0:29:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别跟我讲该死的逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And don't give me any damnable logic
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.07,0:29:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说他是最适合做这件事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about him being the only man for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.83,0:29:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，我不必说，我们心里都明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't have to, Bones. We both know he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.60,0:32:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.31,0:32:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你们会觉得这个东西很有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe you'll find this interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.65,0:32:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，你的医术和好奇心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, your medical skill and curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.82,0:32:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,都让我很钦佩，但是我向你保证，我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are quite admirable, but I assure you, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.95,0:32:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你或许能控制疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You may be controlling the pain, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.53,0:32:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你离康复还差得远呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you're far from all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.83,0:32:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，这件事现在不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unimportant at the moment, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.79,0:32:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意观察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.25,0:32:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣吧，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.01,0:32:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个单细胞生物，竟然比其他任何事物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A one-cell creature resembling, more than anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.01,0:33:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都更像一个巨型的个体脑细胞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a huge individual brain cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.17,0:33:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这就已经能说明很多问题了，是不是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, that would answer a lot of questions, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.58,0:33:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，你明白我的意思了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you understand what I'm suggesting, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.32,0:33:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.50,0:33:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这或许是一个体积更大生物的一个细胞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This may be one cell in a larger organism,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.89,0:33:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上，应该是一个巨大无比的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an incredibly huge organism, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.18,0:33:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，尽管它并没有和其他细胞结合在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And although it is not physically connected to the other cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.06,0:33:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但可以肯定，它一定是那整个生物的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it is, nevertheless, part of the whole creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.07,0:33:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,由整体指挥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Guided by the whole, drawing its strength
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.73,0:33:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从整体中获得力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the whole, which probably accounts
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.32,0:33:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这或许能解释它对我们相位枪的异常抵抗力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for its unusual resistance to our phaser weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.91,0:33:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,它们如此特别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Existing so differently
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.37,0:33:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们所知的任何生命或能量形式都不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from any living matter or energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.66,0:33:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它们或许来自一个完全不同的星系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as we know it that it may have come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.04,0:33:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,经过一颗颗星球，来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}planet by planet, from an entirely different galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.29,0:33:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个地方，我们的物理定律不能适用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From a place where our physical laws do not apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.59,0:33:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们还发现很难毁灭它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We may therefore find it difficult to destroy, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.51,0:33:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是不可能，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not impossible, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.30,0:33:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个飞向太阳的戴内瓦星人最后哭喊着说他自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Denevan that flew into the sun cried out that he was free,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.93,0:33:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他获胜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that he had won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.31,0:33:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，这是一个很好的研究方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the angle to work on, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.60,0:34:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要医学和生命科学部门在一小时内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want an analysis of all this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.40,0:34:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对这一切进行分析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from Medical and Life Science departments within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.07,0:34:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.71,0:34:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.06,0:34:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我很抱歉，我已经试了所有的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, captain. I've tried everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.56,0:34:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不同的辐射，甚至高达9000度的高温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Varying radiation, intense heat, even as great as 9,000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.78,0:34:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在浪费时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.24,0:34:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有一种方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has to be something that will kill the creature
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.28,0:34:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,既能杀死那种生物又不会伤害到人类宿主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without destroying the human host.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.66,0:34:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我想要说的，这种生物杀不死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which happens to be my point: The thing won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.33,0:34:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,即使用能把史波克和你外甥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even at temperatures and radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.99,0:34:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,烧成灰烬的高温和射线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which would burn Spock and your nephew to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.50,0:35:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，我不能接受你的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't accept that, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.12,0:35:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘星舰上有14个科学实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've got 14 science labs aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.46,0:35:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个星系最好的设备和计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The finest equipment and computers in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.17,0:35:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.13,0:35:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解你的忧虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.89,0:35:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你对史波克的爱戴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your affection for Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.51,0:35:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你侄子是你哥哥一家唯一的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the fact that your nephew is the last survivor of your brother's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.52,0:35:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不止两个人的性命堪忧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's more than two lives at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.61,0:35:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让它扩散到殖民地外面去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot let it spread beyond this colony,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.69,0:35:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,即使这意味着…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even if it means destroying...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,…要牺牲星球上的一百万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...a million people down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.71,0:35:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3289.8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3289.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.01,0:35:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我正面临着人生最艰难的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am faced with the most difficult decision of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.89,0:35:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们能找到方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unless we find a way to destroy the creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.56,0:35:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,既能消灭那些生物，又不会伤害到人类宿主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without killing their human hosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.85,0:35:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我作为指挥官的职责就会迫使我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my command responsibilities will force me to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.98,0:35:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,牺牲上百万人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}over a million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.19,0:36:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.94,0:36:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，很遗憾你没有其他的选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I regret I see no other choice for you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.61,0:36:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,据我们所知，这种生物已经摧毁了三种文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We already know this thing has destroyed three civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.11,0:36:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 或许更多 - 先生们，我也想消灭它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- perhaps more. - Gentlemen, I want it stopped too,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.03,0:36:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不是用100多万人的生命做代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but not at the cost of destroying over a million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.54,0:36:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,包括我自己，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Including myself, doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.54,0:36:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还有寇克舰长的侄子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and Captain Kirk's young nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.46,0:36:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解你的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Understandably upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.92,0:36:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一旦它从这里扩散出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But once it spreads past here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.42,0:36:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,它将控制几十个殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there are dozens of colonies beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.55,0:36:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感染数十亿人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and billions of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.30,0:36:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果杀5个人能救10个人，我们就该去做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If killing five people saves ten, it's a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.56,0:36:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，这就是你的简单逻辑吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that your simple logic, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.93,0:36:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，两者我都不会选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will accept neither of those alternatives, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.02,0:36:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让这种生物从这颗星球上扩散出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot let this thing expand beyond this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.98,0:36:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会为了阻止它杀害100万或更多的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nor do I intend to kill a million or more people to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.07,0:36:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要另一种办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want another answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.24,0:36:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你们俩也和我一起思考\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm putting you gentlemen on the hot seat with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要第三种方法！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want that third alternative!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.25,0:37:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我报告 - 吉姆，抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Report. - I'm sorry, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.17,0:37:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经一遍遍看过报告了，任何可能性都测试过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been over it and over it, we've made every conceivable test.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.05,0:37:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我才请求批准将我传送到星球表面上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I therefore request permission to beam down to the planet's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.30,0:37:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我还建议你的侄子跟我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I also suggest your nephew accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.55,0:37:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不批准你的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.93,0:37:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.14,0:37:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是轻率得做出请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not make this request lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.77,0:37:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道自己还能抵抗这种疼痛多长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do not know how much longer I can hold out against the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.77,0:37:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道如果那个男孩恢复意识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I do know what the boy will go through
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.61,0:37:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他也会经历这种疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}should he regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.44,0:37:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不批准\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Request denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一定还有其他的解决方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There must be another answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.12,0:37:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个戴内瓦星人死之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something in the sun killed that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.62,0:37:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳里的东西就已经杀死了那种生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before the Denevan died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.29,0:37:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.21,0:37:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经试过了高温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've tried heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.63,0:37:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,射线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.64,0:37:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳还有什么其他的特性或属性？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What other qualities or properties does the sun have?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.64,0:38:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它是真实存在的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It exists physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.81,0:38:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,它占据空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It occupies space.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.48,0:38:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,它是物质构成的，因此有重力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has mass, therefore gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.57,0:38:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它将物质转化为能量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It converts matter to energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.91,0:38:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我们一遍又一遍地研究过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, we've been through it and through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,辐射，高温…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Radiation, heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有一种东西你们没有提到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But one other thing you haven't mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.08,0:38:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.41,0:38:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你靠得足够近的话，它会发出强光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It radiates a blinding light, if you're close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.96,0:38:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,光不会致命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing lethal about light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.70,0:38:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是对我们，而是对星球地面上的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not to us. But down on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.67,0:38:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那种生物，大部分都待在阴暗处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the creatures stayed in the shadows, for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.05,0:38:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,假设他们并不是简单地为了躲避\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suppose that they weren't simply hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.72,0:38:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,假设他们对某些光很敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suppose they're sensitive to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说离太阳足够近时的太阳光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Light, like in a sun, close up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.77,0:38:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.61,0:38:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你不能把戴内瓦星搬到接近太阳的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't move Deneva closer to the sun, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.19,0:38:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但我们可以把等同于太阳光的东西送到戴内瓦星上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, but you can move the equivalent of the sun to Deneva.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克先生？ - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mr. Spock? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我们可以实现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In essence, it can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一圈围绕着行星的卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A string of satellites around the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.45,0:38:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,携带燃烧着的三菱镁矿和三锕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with burning trimagnesite and trevium.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.87,0:39:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我可以在生物实验室弄一个试验间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I can rig a test cubicle in the bio lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.04,0:39:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们的样本放到里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}put our specimen in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.42,0:39:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但我不… - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- but I don't-- - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.67,0:39:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's get on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.85,0:39:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你确信你的计算是正确的吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your figures are, of course, accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.02,0:39:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.82,0:39:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个戴内瓦星人说他解放了的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The light of the sun at the proximity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其附近太阳的亮度相当于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the Denevan declared himself free
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.90,0:39:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在每平方英寸点燃100万根蜡烛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was 1 million candles per square inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这办法行的通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this works,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.99,0:39:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发射的卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the satellites we orbit will produce light
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.16,0:39:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,将产生亮度非常高的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of such intensity that even someone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在封闭、阴暗地方的人也会受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a closed, darkened area will be affected by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.71,0:39:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.21,0:39:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,带上眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put on your masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.93,0:40:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,试验结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.69,0:40:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,起作用了，我们找到对付他们的方法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It worked! We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.00,0:40:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，你怎么了？我们找到对付他们的方法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the matter, Jim? We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,目前只是在实验室起作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It worked in a lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.79,0:40:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那个生物没有任何遮挡或保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the creature exposed to everything we can give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.84,0:40:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这会对被感染的人产生什么影响？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what about the people who are infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，这或许只是试验性质的，并且——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know. It may be trial and--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.34,0:40:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没时间做假设了，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe. There's no time for maybes, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.55,0:40:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.18,0:40:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不得不——\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I'd have to put--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.93,0:40:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们不得不把一个被感染的人放到光照下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, we'd have to put someone who's infected under that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:40:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这样做有多大的风险吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have any idea of the risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.81,0:40:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须复制那个星球上的环境…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to duplicate the conditions on the planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.65,0:40:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…而且，史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.57,0:40:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.40,0:41:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的下一步试验需要一个宿主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll need a host for the next step in the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.37,0:41:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好判定那种生物是否会被驱逐出身体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to determine whether the creature can be driven from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.83,0:41:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是最适合的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am the logical choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.04,0:41:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道每平方英寸100万根蜡烛点燃的光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what 1-million-candle light per square inch can do
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.92,0:41:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会对你的视觉系统产生什么样的影响吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to your optic nerves?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.71,0:41:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，没有其他的办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no other way, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须复制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to duplicate the brilliance that existed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.72,0:41:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个戴内瓦星人说他解脱时的光强度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the moment the Denevan declared himself free.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.68,0:41:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我给你弄一副防护性的眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. I'll rig up a protective pair of goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.60,0:41:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，星球表面上是不会有那种东西的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There will be none on the planet's surface, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.52,0:41:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也赞同不带眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I agree completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.69,0:41:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是，你们是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, you're both right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.57,0:41:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们唯一可做的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the only thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.53,0:41:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.91,0:42:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生是星舰上最好的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock's the best first officer in the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.12,0:42:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,执行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.94,0:42:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,试验结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.41,0:43:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你还好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.12,0:43:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我身体里的那个生物已经消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The creature within me is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.34,0:43:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我摆脱了它，也摆脱了疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am free of it and the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.47,0:43:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,并且我也…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I am also...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.34,0:43:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,…失明了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...quite blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.60,0:43:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，这是笔公平的交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An equitable trade, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.64,0:43:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.19,0:43:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，对那个生物的首次试验结果依然…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, the results of the first test on the creature's remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.54,0:43:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.09,0:43:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.21,0:44:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我用全光谱照射那个生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I threw the total spectrum of light at the creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.51,0:44:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,其实并不需要那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.59,0:44:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我居然没有停下来思考\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't stop to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是只要一种光就能杀死那种生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only one kind of light might have killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.97,0:44:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.39,0:44:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是狗会对人类听不到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just as dogs are sensitive to certain sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.35,0:44:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,某些声音特别敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which humans cannot hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.52,0:44:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这种生物很明显也对我们看不到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}these creatures evidently are sensitive to light
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.15,0:44:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,光亮特别敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which we cannot see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.86,0:44:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在说…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.20,0:44:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,…史波克先生本不必失明的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that Spock need not have been blinded?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.53,0:44:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我完全可以把致盲的白光屏蔽掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't need to throw the blinding white light at all, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 史波克，我—— - 医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Spock, l-- - Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.88,0:44:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was my selection as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.55,0:44:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,事情已经过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.55,0:44:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.27,0:44:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好好照顾他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.74,0:45:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，正在完成发射轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Completing the seeding orbit, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.70,0:45:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,210颗紫外线卫星已经就位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two hundred and ten ultraviolet satellites now in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.25,0:45:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,高度72英里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}72 miles altitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.42,0:45:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,位于行星永久轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}permanent orbit about the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.54,0:45:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，扫频仪呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. Scanners?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.96,0:45:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官，扫频仪准备好了 - 非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Scanners ready, sir. - Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.84,0:45:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了吗，荷尔姆？ - 准备好了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ready, helm? - Ready, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.26,0:45:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,卫星控制中心，我是舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Satellite control, this is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.60,0:45:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,启动所有卫星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize all satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.93,0:45:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，所有卫星都已启动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All satellites operative, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.64,0:46:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，收到地面站发来的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, receiving messages from a ground station.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.73,0:46:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,汇报情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.56,0:46:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,长官，那些生物变得奄奄一息了，这方法起作用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The things are dying, sir. It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.49,0:46:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,医务室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.16,0:46:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.42,0:46:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉史波克…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.88,0:46:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,…方法起作用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.51,0:46:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.84,0:46:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他听到这条消息会很高兴的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll be happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.85,0:46:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.10,0:47:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,…这不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.19,0:47:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.37,0:47:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,文书，向星舰司令部汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeoman, record this for Starfleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.21,0:47:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官，准备好了 - 戴内瓦星上的外星生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ready, sir. - The alien creatures on Deneva
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.54,0:47:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已全部被消灭—— - 舰长，看，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- have been destroyed-- - Captain, look. Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.05,0:47:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.68,0:47:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.97,0:47:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，失明是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The blindness was temporary, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他的视觉神经\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's something about his optical nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.02,0:47:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和人类的并不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which aren't the same as a human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.15,0:47:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这是一种遗传性状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An hereditary trait, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.44,0:47:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯太阳的亮度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The brightness of the Vulcan sun has caused the development
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.44,0:47:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,使得他们长出了一个内眼睑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of an inner eyelid, which acts as a shield
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.15,0:47:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在遭遇强光照射时会起到遮挡的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}against high-intensity light.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，这完全是本能反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Totally instinctive, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.82,0:48:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会忽略它，就像你会忽略自己的阑尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We tend to ignore it, as you ignore your own appendix.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.75,0:48:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.13,0:48:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,重获光明对多数人来说应该是一次情绪体验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Regaining eyesight would be an emotional experience for most.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.72,0:48:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的没什么感受吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You, I presume, felt nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.60,0:48:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,正好相反，舰长，我有很强烈的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite the contrary, captain. I had a very strong reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.71,0:48:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一眼见到的就是麦考伊医生弯腰俯视我的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My first sight was the face of Dr. McCoy bending over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.36,0:48:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，很遗憾这段短暂失明的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is a pity brief blindness did not increase your appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.66,0:48:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 并没有增加你对美好事物的感激欣赏 - 如果你们说完话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- for beauty, Mr. Spock. - If you gentlemen are finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.25,0:48:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生，你是否介意设定去第十星球基地的路线？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would you mind laying in a course for Starbase 10, Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.92,0:48:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My pleasure, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.87,0:48:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,与众不同的眼睛构造\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unusual eye arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.33,0:48:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道他会那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might've known he'd turn up with something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.09,0:48:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了，医生？ - 我说，不要告诉史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's that, doctor? - I said, please don't tell Spock
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.80,0:48:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过他是星舰上最好的大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I said he was the best first officer in the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.80,0:48:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢，谢谢你，麦考伊医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why, thank you, Dr. McCoy.
